Package: advicegiveR
Type: Package
Title: Generate Advice from the Advice Giver API
Description: This package makes a call to the Advice Giver API to return a string of advice. 
    It can also format the string into an image that you can save. It can be used to make fun cards
    or just generate fun advice for you.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Katie", "Jolly", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "katiejolly6@gmail.com")
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
License: MIT + file LICENSE
BugReports: https://github.com/katiejolly/advicegiveR/issues
Depends:
  magick,
  jsonlite,
  stringr,
  extrafont
Suggests: 
  testthat
